quran[9{c,v,t}:
11,89,"aur ae baradran qoum, mere khilaaf tumhari hatt dharmi kahin yeh nobat nah pouncha day ke aakhir-kaar tum par bhi wohi azaab aa kar rahay jo Nooh ya hood ya saleh ki qoum par aaya tha aur loot ki qoum to tum se kuch ziyada daur bhi nahi hai"
11,90,"dekho! apne rab se maffi mango aur is ki taraf palat aao, be shak mera rab Raheem hai aur apni makhlooq se mohabbat rakhta hai """
11,91,"unhon ne jawab diya"" ae Shoiab, teri bohat si baatein to hamari samajh hi mein nahi aatin aur hum dekhte hain ke to hamaray darmain aik be zor aadmi hai, teri baradri nah hoti to hum kabhi ka tujhe sangsar kar chuke hotay, tera bil bota to itna nahi hai ke hum par bhaari ho """
11,92,"Shoiab ne kaha"" bhayyo, kya meri baradri tum par Allah se ziyada bhaari hai ke tum ne ( baradri ka to khauf kya aur ) Allah ko bilkul pas pusht daal diya? jaan rakho ke jo kuch tum kar rahay ho woh Allah ki girift se bahar nahi hai"
11,93,"ae meri qoum ke logo, tum apne tareeqay par kaam kiye jao aur mein apne tareeqay par karta rahon ga, jaldi hi tumhe maloom ho jaye ga ke kis par zillat ka azaab aata hai aur kon jhoota hai tum bhi intzaar karo aur mein bhi tumahray sath chasham barah hon """
11,94,aakhir-kaar jab hamaray faislay ka waqt aa gaya to hum ne apni rehmat se Shoiab aur is ke saathi mominon ko bacha liya aur jin logon ne zulm kya tha un ko aik sakht dhamakay ne aisa pakra ke woh apni bustiyon mein be hiss o harkat parre ke parre reh gay
11,95,goya woh kabhi wahan rahay basey hi nah thay suno! Mudin walay bhi daur pheink diye gay jis terhan smod phainky gay thay
11,96,aur moose ko hum ne apni nshanyon aur khuli khuli sanad mamooriyat ke sath firaon aur is ke 'Ayanay (uhedaydar)saltanat ki taraf bheja
11,97,magar unhon ne firaon ke hukum ki pairwi ki halaank firaon ka hukum raasti par nah tha
